// checkNegativeContext — silent sound objects rewrite
// Original: -gr.checkNegativeContext (Bernard)
// Terminals: A, A1, A2, A3, B — opaque symbols with negative contexts
RND
gram#1[1] S --> A A2 A3 A1 A A /times=5/
gram#1[2] /times > 0/ #A1 #A2 #A3 A A --> #A1 #A2 A A #A3 /times-1/
gram#1[3] <0> LEFT #A2 #A1 A --> B B
gram#1[4] <0> S --> A
gram#1[5] <0> #B A --> A #B
